{"title":"野百合  （外一首）","authors":["李龙年"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":6,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"野百合（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李龙年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在山涧，在溪畔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在时间的起点，在生命的源头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野百合"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露珠的眸子里晶莹着清澈的太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从纷扰尘世走到这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一粒粒溪卵石使我倍觉温柔温暖！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从3月到12月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百合的旅程写满了祝福的诗句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我只留下最简短的一行——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这清澈，这纯净"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这爱的幸福的子弹……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}